wikipedia_page.main: Arthur Owen Snowden (7 May 1885 – 22 May 1964) was a teacher and an English amateur cricketer. He played in six first-class cricket matches between 1905 and 1912.

response: Sir Arthur Snowden (29 July 1829 – 18 June 1918) was an Australian lawyer, politician and mayor of Melbourne from 1892–95.
